The All-In-One Calendar is a an all inclusive calendar feature that can be easily downloaded and installed to give you a complete calendar solution for your Drupal website.

AIOcalendar requires the [Features module](http://drupal.org/project/features) from [Drupal.org](http://drupal.org).


Installation: 

1: Download AIOCalendar
2: Download dependancies:
drush dl beautytips better_exposed_filters calendar calendar_ical date date_popup features filefield_sources image menu strongarm taxonomy views 
3: Enable AIO Calendar: 


